{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And what these-- what they did was they would have clubs, and they would beat him on the buttocks and legs with these clubs and spin him around on this swing, both directions.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they'd-- there would be a circle of SS guys around him, and as they-- as his buttocks went by, they'd hit him again and the momentum to keep him moving.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then they would stop, and they'd do it the other way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now-- and-- now this is the way they explained this to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very few men survived that because they were hitting the kidneys and, and other places as opposed to-- the idea was to hit him on the buttocks and on the top of their thighs.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's very, very painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And to get them to confess or punish them for something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't have to have a reason.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They just punished them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was probably the weirdest thing that I saw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And another one which was very common, especially at Dachau, well, was making the inmates beat each other with, with sticks and with whips.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was this-- that was kind of like a-- that was a form of recreation for the SS was to get the weaker inmates to be beaten by the stronger inmates or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And if they refused to do it, they were beaten to death by the SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one of the most-- and here, again, I don't understand how anybody could tolerate this-- was, was be like a four by four post stuck in the ground.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- so they would tie a person's hands behind their back, tie their legs together behind their back, and it had a pulley like a, like a water-- like a well would have a pulley to bring up the bucket.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
